item.title: Error when logging in [718]
item.dc:creator: @sk8rdude461 sk8rdude461
item.description:
@sk8rdude461 wrote:

Looks like you’re trying to load something that doesn’t exist (or trying to load from the wrong spot, etc)…

The fix is:
A) Removing the code that is trying to load the file

B) point the code to the correct location of the file

C) Adding/creating the file, then pointing the code to it’s location.
